     and q ~~ t ==> ?u. upoly u /\ (q = u * t)         by poly_unit_eq_property
      so u * t = q = s * p
   Hence ?v. poly v /\ (t = v * (s * p))   by poly_mult_lunit
      or t = v * s * p                     by poly_mult_assoc
